{
  "stem": "9878.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like I was there now in 1989, I was in my hometown simply when my brother-in-law came to Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He told the a real hell of a story that when he came to say Kaddish-- meaning the prayer for the dead on their grave site for his wife and children-- my sister-- he finds skeletons and little bones of babies thrown about all around.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to look around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he find a pair of pants lying there-- painter's pants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took a stick to lift the pants.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Golden teeth fell out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he didn't have to say, one and one, what is happening?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He say, oh, yeah, they're hanging up the skeletons on the-- on the trees.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They marked the dead people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they're digging the graves [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because in Europe, if you lose a tooth, you don't have any plastic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They put gold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Even the poor man collects a few dollars for the golden tooth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they kept on digging, digging, digging the grave site in order to dig out the skeletons to pull the teeth out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we were so incensed-- so incensed of this, that this is happening after so many years, atrocity happening against the Jewish people, that we decided to go and visit Russia, and plead with them.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They should make a national shrine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Close the place up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one woman who was hung because she was a partisan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put a big monument of marble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they spent about a million to beautify the place, one person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here is 28,000 people died, and nobody thinks about protecting the area and putting a monument on it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's only a little stone, like I showed you in the pictures, about the height of my shoulders.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I come into this Russian commissar.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
